### Register User
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/register/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "test",
    "email": "test@mail.com",
    "password": "test@1234",
    "password2": "test@1234"
}

### Login (Obtain Token)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/token/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "test",
    "password": "test@1234"
}

### Refresh Token
